      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHASING SUNSET (7) ran below best last time finishing fifth (20.15) over 350m at this track from Box 1. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. THAI BUTTERFLY (5) produced a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 350m behind Abundant Lumens (19.85) in a Special conditions Veteran race. Was a winner prior to that. Has ability and is one of the better chances. BE A BEAUTY (4) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 16.98 beating Glamorous Gal. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. In top form and looks a key chance again. ROSCOE BALE (1) deserves plenty of thought over this journey.",
